《永恒之柱》由[[黑曜石娱乐|黑曜石娱乐]]开发、[[Paradox_Interactive|Paradox Interactive]]发行，<ref>{{cite news|title=Pillars of Eternity Game-Breaking Bug Alert|url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/140282-Pillars-of-Eternity-has-a-Game-Breaking-Bug|first=Heather |last=Barefoot |access-date=2015-04-01|work=[[The_Escapist|The Escapist]]|date= 2015-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402110021/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/140282-Pillars-of-Eternity-has-a-Game-Breaking-Bug|archive-date=2015-04-02|url-status=dead}}</ref>采用为游戏特别定制的[[Unity_(游戏引擎)|Unity]]引擎完成开发，<ref name="secondkick">{{cite news|last1=Carlson|first1=Patrick|title=Obsidian considering a second Kickstarter campaign after Pillars of Eternity|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/12/19/obsidian-working-towards-a-second-post-pillars-of-eternity-kickstarter/|access-date=2015-04-01|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|date= 2013-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122051038/http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/12/19/obsidian-working-towards-a-second-post-pillars-of-eternity-kickstarter/|archive-date= 2014-01-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=King|first1=Channing|title='Pillars of Eternity,' 'Bloodborne' highlight digital week|url=http://www.indystar.com/story/entertainment/2015/03/27/pillars-eternity-bloodborne-highlight-digital-week/70555278/|access-date= 2021-11-16|work=[[The_Indianapolis_Star|The Indianapolis Star]]|date= 2015-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150517210614/http://www.indystar.com/story/entertainment/2015/03/27/pillars-eternity-bloodborne-highlight-digital-week/70555278/?from=global&sessionKey=&autologin=|archive-date=2015-05-17|url-status=live}}</ref>并由{{le|乔什·索亚|Josh Sawyer}}担任游戏总监。<ref>{{cite news|title=Pillars of Eternity video: Josh Sawyer on character creation and Infinity RPGs|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/pillars-of-eternity-video-josh-sawyer-on-character-creation-and-infinity-rpgs/|author=PCGamer|access-date=2021-11-16|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|date= 2014-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402100321/http://www.pcgamer.com/pillars-of-eternity-video-josh-sawyer-on-character-creation-and-infinity-rpgs/|archive-date= 2015-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref>起初黑曜石娱乐内部对游戏的剧情构想意见不一，最终埃里克·芬斯特马克（Eric Fenstermaker）和[[乔治·兹亚茨|乔治·兹亚茨]]的版本获得青睐，曾为《[[辐射：新维加斯|辐射：新维加斯]]》撰写剧本的芬斯特马克随后出任首席编剧一职。<ref name="RPGCEFI">{{cite web|author=Infinitron|title=RPG Codex Interview: Eric Fenstermaker on Pillars of Eternity|url=http://www.rpgcodex.net/content.php?id=10231|access-date= 2021-11-16|publisher=RPG Codex|date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211107223827/https://rpgcodex.net/content.php?id=10231|archive-date=2021-11-07|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=writerguildsutra>{{cite web|last1=Wawro|first1=Alex|title=Pillars of Eternity, Witcher 3 among Writer's Guild award nominees|url=http://gamasutra.com/view/news/263340/Pillars_of_Eternity_Witcher_3_among_Writers_Guild_award_nominees.php|access-date= 2021-11-16|website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|date= 2016-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108180026/https://www.gamedeveloper.com/business/-i-pillars-of-eternity-i-i-witcher-3-i-among-writer-s-guild-award-nominees|archive-date=2021-11-08|url-status=live}}</ref>亚当·布伦内克（Adam Brennecke）、{{le|克里斯·阿维隆|Chris Avellone}}和{{le|蒂姆·坎|Tim Cain}}也参与了游戏制作。<ref name="DreamRPG">{{cite web|last1=Schreier|first1=Jason|title=The People Behind Fallout And Planescape Are Making My Dream RPG|url=http://kotaku.com/5942307/the-people-behind-fallout-and-planescape-are-making-my-dream-rpg|website=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|access-date=2021-11-16|date= 2012-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416052651/http://kotaku.com/5942307/the-people-behind-fallout-and-planescape-are-making-my-dream-rpg|archive-date=2015-04-16|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="Expansion">{{cite news|last1=Yin-Poole|first1=Wesley|title=Big Pillars of Eternity expansion already in the works|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-03-17-big-pillars-of-eternity-expansion-already-in-the-works|access-date= 2021-11-16|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date= 2015-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402184925/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-03-17-big-pillars-of-eternity-expansion-already-in-the-works|archive-date= 2015-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref>游戏配乐由贾斯廷·E·贝尔（Justin E. Bell）负责，他也是《永恒之柱》的音频总监。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Carlson|first1=Patrick|title=Pillars of Eternity soundtrack previewed in music release|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/pillars-of-eternity-soundtrack-previewed-in-music-release/|website=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|access-date=2021-11-16|date= 2014-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150517210831/http://www.pcgamer.com/pillars-of-eternity-soundtrack-previewed-in-music-release/|archive-date= 2015-05-17|url-status=live}}</ref>贝尔表示自己在创作游戏配乐时，从《[[博德之门系列|博德之门]]》和《[[冰风谷系列|冰风谷]]》的音乐中受益良多。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Prell|first1=S.|title=Obsidian gives your ears a taste of the Pillars of Eternity soundtrack|url=https://www.engadget.com/2014/04/16/obsidian-gives-your-ears-a-taste-of-the-pillars-of-eternity-soun/|publisher=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|access-date=2021-11-16|date= 2014-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108010938/https://www.engadget.com/2014-04-16-obsidian-gives-your-ears-a-taste-of-the-pillars-of-eternity-soun.html|archive-date= 2021-11-08|url-status=live}}</ref>

2012年9月10日，黑曜石娱乐在其官网放出代号“项目X”（Project X）的新游戏预告图，图中有一条[[衔尾蛇|衔尾蛇]]环绕着数字4，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/11/obsidian-teasing-mysterious-project-x|title=Obsidian Teasing Mysterious "Project X"|last=Reilly|first=Luke|date=2012-09-10|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403172608/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/11/obsidian-teasing-mysterious-project-x|archive-date= 2015-04-03|url-status=live}}</ref>人们在次日发现这是个倒计时。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/12/obsidians-countdown-continues-with-new-details|title=Obsidian's Countdown Continues With New Details|last=Karmali|first=Luke|date=2012-09-12|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403172553/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/12/obsidians-countdown-continues-with-new-details|archive-date=2015-04-03|url-status=live}}</ref>到了9月14日，正式的[[众筹|众筹]]活动在[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]发布，展示了更多项目内容。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/14/obsidians-fantasy-rpg-reveals-founders-true-desires|title=Obsidian's Fantasy RPG Reveals Founders' True Desires|last=Campbell|first=Colin|date= 2012-09-14|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120918060601/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/14/obsidians-fantasy-rpg-reveals-founders-true-desires|archive-date=2012-09-18 |url-status=live}}</ref>项目最初设定的110万美元目标在短短24小时内达到，工作室随即宣布了第一阶段延伸目标。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pc.gamespy.com/pc/project-eternity/1226102p1.html|title=Project Eternity Funded in Just Over 24 Hours, Obsidian Outlines Stretch Goals|last=Sharkey|first=Mike|date=2012-09-17|publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402103735/http://pc.gamespy.com/pc/project-eternity/1226102p1.html|archive-date= 2015-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref>项目发布五天后，筹款已超过160万美元，<ref name="Kickstarter1909"/>随后在9月26日突破200万美元大关。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/119813-Project-Eternity-Breaks-2-Million|title=Project Eternity Breaks $2 Million|last=Chalk|first=Andy|date=2012-09-26|work=[[The_Escapist|The Escapist]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402183426/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/119813-Project-Eternity-Breaks-2-Million|archive-date= 2015-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref>工作室表示游戏将会登陆[[OS_X|OS X]]平台，并于[[GOG.com|GOG]]上提供无[[数字版权管理|DRM]]选项的版本，<ref name="Kickstarter1909">{{cite web|url=http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/obsidian/project-eternity/posts/311594|title=Update #4 – Digital Tiers, DRM, and Add-Ons Update|last=Urquhart|first=Feargus|date= 2012-09-19|publisher=[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402192511/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/obsidian/project-eternity/posts/311594|archive-date= 2015-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref>又在9月21日承诺推出[[Linux|Linux]]版本游戏。<ref name="Kickstarter2109">{{cite web|url=http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/obsidian/project-eternity/posts/313192|title=Update #6 – Choosing the Best Tool for the Job|last=Jones|first=Chris|date= 2012-09-21|publisher=[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402101448/http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/obsidian/project-eternity/posts/313192|archive-date= 2015-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref>黑曜石娱乐在10月8日宣布，将向所有投资达到165美元的支持者提供另一款游戏《{{le|废土2|Wasteland 2}}》作为奖励。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Purchese|first1=Robert|title=Project Eternity adds Wasteland 2 as tiered Kickstarter reward|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-10-09-project-eternity-adds-wasteland-2-as-tiered-kickstarter-reward|access-date= 2021-11-16|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date= 2012-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403053410/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-10-09-project-eternity-adds-wasteland-2-as-tiered-kickstarter-reward|archive-date=2015-04-03|url-status=live}}</ref>众筹活动进入最后一天，项目筹资金额已然超越《[[破碎时光|破碎时光]]》，成为当时在Kickstarter上筹资最多的游戏。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/gaming/2012/10/15/3507318/project-eternity|title='Project Eternity' surpasses 'Double Fine Adventure' to become Kickstarter's most-funded video game|last=Tach|first=Dave|date=2012-10-15|publisher=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016194847/http://www.theverge.com/gaming/2012/10/15/3507318/project-eternity|archive-date= 2012-10-16|url-status=live}}</ref>

2012年10月16日，游戏在Kickstarter上的众筹活动宣告结束，项目最终共筹得3,986,929美元开发经费。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/obsidian/project-eternity?lang=zh|title=Project Eternity by Obsidian Entertainment|publisher=[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]|date=2018-05-12|accessdate=2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210202121/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/obsidian/project-eternity?lang=zh|archive-date=2021-12-10|url-status=no}}</ref>再加上通过[[PayPal|PayPal]]收集到的资金，整个游戏的预算增至4,163,208美元。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-10-17-a-project-eternity-recap-what-USD4-million-has-funded|title=A Project Eternity recap: what $4 million has funded|last=Purchese|first=Robert|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date= 2012-10-17|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141115205053/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-10-17-a-project-eternity-recap-what-USD4-million-has-funded|archive-date= 2014-11-15 |url-status=live}}</ref>黑曜石娱乐于2013年12月将游戏正式定名为《永恒之柱》，取代众筹期间使用的临时名称《永恒计划》（Project Eternity）。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Grayson|first1=Nathan|title=Mega-Impressions: Obsidian's Pillars Of Eternity|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/12/10/mega-impressions-obsidians-pillars-of-eternity/|website=[[Rock_Paper_Shotgun|Rock Paper Shotgun]]|access-date=2021-11-16|date= 2013-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141222135415/http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/12/10/mega-impressions-obsidians-pillars-of-eternity/|archive-date=2014-12-22|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="propervideo">{{cite news|last1=Purchese|first1=Robert|title=Obsidian renames Project Eternity, releases a proper video|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-12-10-obsidian-renames-project-eternity-releases-a-proper-video|access-date= 2021-11-16|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date= 2013-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403043309/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-12-10-obsidian-renames-project-eternity-releases-a-proper-video|archive-date= 2015-04-03|url-status=live}}</ref>他们还发起了一项[[民意调查|民意调查]]，询问支持者们是否愿意接受进一步筹款。<ref name="propervideo"/>

2010年代初，资深游戏开发商往往会在玩家怀旧心理驱动下发起众筹活动，迫使主要发行商为可能已经过时的小众游戏类型提供开发资金，《永恒之柱》也不例外。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Gilbert|first=Andrew Simon|date=2017|title=Crowdfunding Nostalgia: Kickstarter and the Revival of Classic PC Game Genres|journal=The Computer Games Journal|language=en|volume=6|issue=1–2|pages=17–32|doi=10.1007/s40869-017-0031-x|s2cid=8094324|issn=2052-773X}}</ref>黑曜石娱乐的[[首席执行官|CEO]]{{le|费格斯·厄克特|Feargus Urquhart}}曾就游戏为何采用众筹模式而非传统的开发商与发行商对接作出解释：“Kickstarter能让我们做出一款绝对致敬经典的游戏，传统发行商却不肯拿出这么多的资金。”<ref name="GameBanshee1409">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamebanshee.com/interviews/109456-project-eternity-interview.html|title=Project Eternity Interview|author=BuckGB|date=2012-09-14|publisher=GameBanshee|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150125111837/http://www.gamebanshee.com/interviews/109456-project-eternity-interview.html|archive-date= 2015-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref>游戏总监乔什·索亚也曾在采访中表示，没有发行商的限制，可以让他们“深入探讨更富争议的话题，包括奴隶制，涉及种族、文化、意识形态和性别的敌对偏见，毒品的使用与交易，以及其他有助于充实故事的内容。”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2012/09/project-eternitys-all-star-effort-to-revive-the-classic-pc-rpg/|title=Project Eternity's all-star effort to revive the classic PC RPG|first=Kyle |last=Orland|date=2012-09-21|work=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140117043039/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2012/09/project-eternitys-all-star-effort-to-revive-the-classic-pc-rpg/|archive-date= 2014-01-17|url-status=live}}</ref>黑曜石娱乐承认他们受到[[inXile娱乐|inXile娱乐]]通过Kickstarter为《废土2》众筹成功的鼓舞，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2012/09/21/project_eternity_kickstarter_obsidian_entertainment_interview/|title=Project Eternity interview: Obsidian on making RPGs awesome again|last=Cook|first=Dave|date=2012-09-21|website=[[VG247|VG247]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402115409/http://www.vg247.com/2012/09/21/project_eternity_kickstarter_obsidian_entertainment_interview/|archive-date=2015-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref>曾领导开发《[[异域镇魂曲|异域镇魂曲]]》的克里斯·阿维隆更在项目发布期间表示，倘若此次众筹活动取得成功，他们将把《永恒之柱》打造成一个系列。但阿维隆也否决了将游戏移植到[[家用机|家用机]]的可能，他直言“家用机自身局限对[[电子角色扮演游戏|RPG]]机制和内容的影响远超玩家们预想，尤其对于那些从未接触过CRPG、不知道自己错过了什么的玩家而言，家用机通常无法带来良好的RPG游玩体验。”<ref name="DreamRPG"/>尽管如此，游戏最终还是成功移植到了家用机上。<ref name="GSpecexp8"/>此外，阿维隆还承诺以游戏世界为背景创作中篇小说，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/danielnyegriffiths/2012/09/26/project-eternity-chris-avellone-kickstarter/|title=Contemplating Eternity: Chris Avellone Talks Sales, Souls and (Kick)Starts|author=Nye Griffiths, Daniel|date=2012-09-26|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402144459/http://www.forbes.com/sites/danielnyegriffiths/2012/09/26/project-eternity-chris-avellone-kickstarter/|archive-date= 2015-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref>如今已有四部中篇小说发布于黑曜石娱乐官网。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://eternity.obsidian.net/eternity/media/stories|title=Short Stories|publisher=[[Obsidian_Entertainment|Obsidian Entertainment]]|access-date=2021-11-16|archive-date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210020413/http://eternity.obsidian.net/eternity/media/stories|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[Paradox_Interactive|Paradox Interactive]]于2014年3月正式确定为《永恒之柱》的发行商。据悉，Paradox将专注于游戏的市场营销和分销工作，黑曜石娱乐依然保有游戏全部[[知识产权|知识产权]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-03-18-paradox-publishing-pillars-of-eternity-obsidians-explanation|title=Obsidian partners with Paradox for Pillars of Eternity|last=Purchese|first=Robert|date=2014-03-18|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|access-date=2021-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140415164849/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-03-18-paradox-publishing-pillars-of-eternity-obsidians-explanation|archive-date=2014-04-15 |url-status=live}}</ref>2015年3月11日，黑曜石娱乐发布了名为《永恒之路》（Road to Eternity）的系列纪录片为游戏发售预热，主要讲述《永恒之柱》的诞生历程。纪录片揭示了《永恒之柱》之于黑曜石娱乐的重要意义：早在2012年，工作室曾为次世代家用机开发一款大型游戏，但项目中途取消，公司遭遇财务危机且面临倒闭，正是《永恒之柱》在Kickstarter众筹成功所带来的资金挽救了这一切。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/03/11/pillars-of-eternity-saved-obisidan-from-closure/|title=Pillars of Eternity saved Obisidan from closure|first=Brenna |last=Hillier|website=[[VG247|VG247]]|date= 2015-03-11|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402171726/http://www.vg247.com/2015/03/11/pillars-of-eternity-saved-obisidan-from-closure/|archive-date= 2015-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-03-11-before-pillars-of-eternity-obsidian-nearly-met-its-end|title=Before Pillars of Eternity, Obsidian nearly met its end|author=Robert Purchese|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2015-03-11|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150314220728/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-03-11-before-pillars-of-eternity-obsidian-nearly-met-its-end|archive-date= 2015-03-14 |url-status=live}}</ref>

==发行==
2015年3月17日，黑曜石娱乐证实《永恒之柱》的开发工作已经结束，正在为即将到来的发售做准备。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/03/17/pillars-of-eternity-gold-linux-mac-pc/|title=Pillars of Eternity has gone gold|last=Hillier|first=Brenna|website=[[VG247|VG247]]|date= 2015-03-17|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402132240/http://www.vg247.com/2015/03/17/pillars-of-eternity-gold-linux-mac-pc/|archive-date= 2015-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref>游戏随后于3月26日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[OS_X|OS X]]和[[Linux|Linux]]平台正式发售。<ref>{{cite news|last=Savage|first=Phil|date= 2015-01-14|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/pillars-of-eternity-release-date-announced/|title=Pillars of Eternity release date announced|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150116221006/http://www.pcgamer.com/pillars-of-eternity-release-date-announced/|archive-date= 2015-01-16|url-status=live}}</ref>游戏同时发行多个版本：冠军版（Champion Edition）包含了游戏世界地图和历史年鉴，游戏[[原声带|原声带]]、壁纸及铃声；皇家版（Royal Edition）在冠军版基础上增加游戏战略指南、概念艺术，以及克里斯·阿维隆为游戏创作的中篇小说。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Fuller|first1=Alex|title=Obsidian's Pillars of Eternity Now Complete|url=http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q1-2015/032615d.html|publisher=[[RPGamer|RPGamer]]|access-date= 2015-04-02|date= 2015-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402194827/http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q1-2015/032615d.html|archive-date=2015-04-02|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Tan|first1=Nicholas|title=Pillars of Eternity Goes Gold, Ready for Launch on March 26|url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/news/pillars-of-eternity-goes-gold-ready-for-launch-on-march-26-31803|publisher=[[Game_Revolution|Game Revolution]]|access-date= 2021-11-16|date= 2015-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402181916/http://www.gamerevolution.com/news/pillars-of-eternity-goes-gold-ready-for-launch-on-march-26-31803|archive-date= 2015-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref>游戏的完整版本《永恒之柱：完整版》（Pillars of Eternity: Complete Edition）于2017年8月29日登陆[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台，该版本由Paradox Arctic移植，包含了游戏本体更新及所有资料片内容。<ref name="GSpecexp8">{{cite web|last1=Fillari|first1=Alessandro|title=Pillars Of Eternity: Complete Edition Coming To Consoles, Launching August 29|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/pillars-of-eternity-complete-edition-coming-to-con/1100-6451064/|access-date= 2021-11-16|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date= 2017-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170621161958/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/pillars-of-eternity-complete-edition-coming-to-con/1100-6451064/|archive-date=2017-06-21|url-status=live}}</ref>游戏的[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]版本于2019年8月8日推出，交由{{le|Versus Evil|Versus Evil}}负责发行，<ref name="auto"/>但因为始终无法修复的重大[[程序错误|程序错误]]，Versus Evil最终于2021年2月8日宣布放弃游戏在Switch的移植工作。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pillars of Eternity’s Switch port won’t be getting any better|url=https://www.polygon.com/2021/2/9/22274651/pillars-of-eternity-nintendo-switch-port-technical-issues-update|first=Charlie |last=Hall |publisher=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|date=2021-02-09|accessdate=2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211113113717/https://www.polygon.com/2021/2/9/22274651/pillars-of-eternity-nintendo-switch-port-technical-issues-update|archive-date=2021-11-13|url-status=live}}</ref>

