黑曜石娱乐于2016年5月确认了《永恒之柱》续作的开发计划，可能会再次通过众筹募集资金。<ref name="WRes27">{{cite news|last1=Whitaker|first1=Ron|title=Pillars of Eternity II is in Development, says Obsidian CEO|url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/167459-Pillars-of-Eternity-2-in-Development-at-Obsidian-CEO-Confirms|access-date= 2017-08-03|work=[[The_Escapist|The Escapist]]|date= 2016-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128063719/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/167459-Pillars-of-Eternity-2-in-Development-at-Obsidian-CEO-Confirms|archive-date=2017-01-28|url-status=dead}}</ref>2017年1月26日，续作正式定名为《{{le|永恒之柱2：死亡之火|Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire}}》，同时在{{le|Fig (公司)|Fig (company)|Fig}}开启众筹活动，不到一天时间就完成了既定的110万美元目标，<ref name="eurogamer_announce">{{cite web | url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-01-26-pillars-of-eternity-2-deadfire-announced | title=Pillars of Eternity 2: Deadfire announced | work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | first=Wesley | last=Yin-Poole | date=2017-01-26 | access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211113121526/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-01-26-pillars-of-eternity-2-deadfire-announced|archive-date=2021-11-13|url-status=live}}</ref>活动结束时共计筹得超过440万美元开发经费。<ref name="gamespot_end">{{cite web | url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/pillars-of-eternity-2-fig-funding-ends-with-44-mil/1100-6448199/ | title=Pillars Of Eternity 2 Fig Funding Ends With $4.4 Million [UPDATE] | work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | first=Eddie | last=Makuch | date= 2017-02-25 | access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211113124324/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/pillars-of-eternity-2-fig-funding-ends-with-44-mil/1100-6448199/|archive-date=2021-11-13|url-status=live}}</ref>《死亡之火》改由{{le|Versus Evil|Versus Evil}}发行，<ref name="vseleg1">{{cite news|last=Purchese|first=Robert|date=2017-09-21|title=Pillars of Eternity 2: Deadfire signs publisher Versus Evil|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-09-21-pillars-of-eternity-2-deadfire-signs-publisher-versus-evil|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|access-date=2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211113132116/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-09-21-pillars-of-eternity-2-deadfire-signs-publisher-versus-evil|archive-date=2021-11-13|url-status=live}}</ref>于2018年5月8日在Microsoft Windows、OS X和Linux平台发售，<ref name="vg247k18">{{cite news|last1=Nunneley|first1=Stephany|title=Pillars of Eternity 2: Deadfire releases in April – here's information on available editions and preorders|url=https://www.vg247.com/2018/01/26/pillars-of-eternity-2-deadfire-releases-in-april-heres-information-on-available-editions-and-preorders/|access-date= 2021-11-16|work=[[VG247|VG247]]|date= 2018-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126184138/https://www.vg247.com/2018/01/26/pillars-of-eternity-2-deadfire-releases-in-april-heres-information-on-available-editions-and-preorders/|archive-date= 2018-01-26|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="ginfk18">{{cite news|last1=Vazquez|first1=Suriel|title=Pillars Of Eternity II: Deadfire Launching On PC In April, Special Editions Announced|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2018/01/25/pillars-of-eternity-ii-deadfire-launching-on-pc-in-april-special-editions-announced.aspx|access-date= 2021-11-16|work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|date= 2018-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180127155343/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2018/01/25/pillars-of-eternity-ii-deadfire-launching-on-pc-in-april-special-editions-announced.aspx|archive-date= 2018-01-27|url-status=live}}</ref>而后于2020年1月28日登陆PlayStation 4和Xbox One平台。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://versusevil.com/pillars-of-eternity-en/pillars-of-eternity-ii-deadfire-ultimate-edition-available-now-on-playstation-4-and-xbox-one/|title=Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire – Ultimate Edition Available Now on PlayStation 4 and Xbox One|author=Versus Evil|publisher={{le|Versus Evil|Versus Evil}}|date=2020-01-28|accessdate=2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211113124250/https://versusevil.com/pillars-of-eternity-en/pillars-of-eternity-ii-deadfire-ultimate-edition-available-now-on-playstation-4-and-xbox-one/|archive-date=2021-11-13|url-status=live}}</ref>游戏故事发生在前作五年后，被认为已死的俄撒斯神自努亚堡地底苏醒，主角“灵视者”在对抗中身负重伤，临死之际被死亡与轮回之神贝拉斯救起，代价则是替贝拉斯前往遥远的亡焰列岛，追捕俄撒斯并找出他的计划。<ref name="vg247_announce">{{cite web | url=https://www.vg247.com/2017/01/26/pillars-of-eternity-2-deadfire-in-development-crowdfunding-campaign-kicks-off-on-fig/ | title=Pillars of Eternity 2: Deadfire in development, crowdfunding campaign kicks off on Fig | work=[[VG247|VG247]] | first=Stephany | last=Nunneley | date= 2017-01-26 | access-date= 2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211113131128/https://www.vg247.com/pillars-of-eternity-2-deadfire-in-development-crowdfunding-campaign-kicks-off-on-fig|archive-date=2021-11-13|url-status=live}}</ref>

